|raisemaxlevel=5\n|skill=Eject\n|skilldesc=Removes one non-Support Pokémon icon without fail.\n}}\n{{Spindata/Shuffle|col=3|type=Ghost|ndex=711Spooky|num=321\n|min=60\n|max=105\n|raisemaxlevel=5\n|skill=Spookify\n|skilldesc=Leaves the foe spooked.\n}}\n|}\n\n===Evolution===\n{{Evobox-2\n|type1=ghost\n|type2=grass\n|pictype=art\n|no1=710\n|name1=Pumpkaboo\n|type1-1=Ghost\n|type2-1=Grass\n|evo1={{bag|Pal Pad}}<br>{{color2|000|Trade}}\n|no2=711\n|name2=Gourgeist\n|type1-2=Ghost\n|type2-2=Grass}}\n\n===Sprites===\n{{Spritebox/Header|type=ghost|type2=grass}}\n{{Spritebox/NA|gen=VI}}\n{{Spritebox/6/4Forms|ndex=711|form1=Sm|form2=La|form3=Su}}\n{{Spritebox/7/4Forms|ndex=711|form1=Sm|form2=La|form3=Su}}\n{{Spritebox/Footer|711|Gourgeist}}\n\n==Trivia==\n* A Super Size Gourgeist has a different cry from its other three forms, pitched lower than the cry shared by the other forms.\n* Only Average Size and Super Size Gourgeist can have its Hidden Ability {{a|Insomnia}}. Average Size can be obtained as a Pumpkaboo with its Hidden Ability from the [[Friend Safari]]; Super Size can be obtained as a Pumpkaboo from {{DL|Pumpkaboo (Pokémon)|In events|event distributions}}.\n\n===Origin===\nGourgeist appears to be based on both {{wp|gourd}} and modern pumpkin {{wp|jack-o\'-lantern}}s. Its multiple sizes may be a reference to the tradition of trying to grow the largest pumpkin for Halloween. Its upper body may also be based on the {{wp|candle}}s within jack-o\'-lanterns themselves, with the curl being its wick and its hair-like extensions its dripping wax. It could also be viewed as a mere extension of the shape and the curl on top being its stem. The lower body\'s different color might also reference the tradition of decorating gourds with paint.\n\n====Name origin====\nGourgeist is a combination of \'\'{{wp|gourd}}\'\' and \'\'{{wp|geist}}\'\'.\n\nPumpjin is a combination of \'\'pumpkin\'\' and 神 \'\'{{wp|Shen (Chinese religion)|shin}}\'\' (deity, spirit), 人 \'\'jin\'\' (man), or \'\'{{wp|jinn}}\'\'.\n\n==In other languages==\n{{Other languages|type=ghost|type2=grass\n|ja=パンプジン \'\'Pumpjin\'\'|jameaning=From \'\'pumpkin\'\' and {{tt|神 \'\'shin\'\'|deity, spirit}}, {{tt|人 \'\'jin\'\'|man}}, or \'\'{{wp|jinn}}\'\'\n|fr=Banshitrouye|frmeaning=From \'\'{{wp|banshee}}\'\', \'\'{{tt|citrouille|pumpkin}}\'\', and \'\'{{tt|trouille|fear}}\'\'\n|es=Gourgeist|esmeaning=Same as English name\n|de=Pumpdjinn|demeaning=From \'\'pumpkin\'\' and \'\'{{wp|Jinn|Dschinn}}\'\'\n|it=Gourgeist|itmeaning=Same as English name\n|ko=펌킨인 \'\'Peomkin\'in|komeaning=From \'\'pumpkin\'\' and {{tt|인 (人) \'\'in\'\'|man}}\n|zh_cmn=南瓜怪人 \'\'Nánguāgwaaiyàhn\'\'|zh_cmnmeaning=From {{tt|南瓜 \'\'nánguā\'\'|pumpkin}} and {{tt|怪人 \'\'gwaaiyàhn\'\'|strange being}}\n|hi=गौरगाइस्ट \'\'Gourgeist\'\'|himeaning=Transcription of English name\n|ru=Гургайст \'\'Gurgayst\'\'|rumeaning=Transcription of English name\n}}\n{{-}}\n{| style="float:left"\n|-\n| style="vertical-align:top" |\n\'\'Small Size\'\'\n{{langtable\n|color={{ghost color}}|bordercolor={{grass color dark}}\n|ja=ちいさいサイズ \'\'Small Size\'\'\n|zh_cmn=小體型 \'\'Xiǎo Tǐxíng \'\'\n|fr=Taille Mini\n|de=Größe S\n|it=Forma Mini\n|ko=작은사이즈 \'\'Small Size\'\'\n|es=Tamaño Pequeño\n}}\n| style="vertical-align:top" |\n\'\'Average Size\'\'\n{{langtable\n|color={{ghost color}}|bordercolor={{grass color dark}}\n|ja=ふつうのサイズ \'\'Average Size\'\'\n|zh_cmn=普通體型 \'\'Pǔtōng Tǐxíng \'\'\n|fr=Taille Normale\n|de=Größe M\n|it=Forma Normale\n|ko=보통사이즈 \'\'Normal Size\'\'\n|es=Tamaño Normal\n}}\n|-\n| style="vertical-align:top" |\n\'\'Large Size\'\'\n{{langtable\n|color={{ghost color}}|bordercolor={{grass color dark}}\n|ja=おおきいサイズ \'\'Large Size\'\'\n|zh_cmn=大體型 \'\'Dà Tǐxíng \'\'\n|fr=Taille Maxi\n|de=Größe L\n|it=Forma Grande\n|ko=큰사이즈 \'\'Large Size\'\'\n|es=Tamaño Grande\n}}\n| style="vertical-align:top" |\n\'\'Super Size\'\'\n{{langtable\n|color={{ghost color}}|bordercolor={{grass color dark}}\n|ja=とくだいサイズ \'\'Extra Large Size\'\'\n|zh_cmn=特大體型 \'\'Tèdà Tǐx